{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a641dbf7-db25-48a7-b171-60b356b39bfa","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory. Since I can't inspect your specific workflow, here's what you need to change to switch to **NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC)**:\n\n---\n\n### 1. Configure NuGet.org\nOn [nuget.org](https://www.nuget.org), go to your package → **Manage** → **Publishing policies** → **Trusted publishers**, and add a GitHub Actions provider with your **repo**, **branch/tag filter**, and **workflow filename**.\n\n### 2. Update your workflow\n\n**Add an `id-token` permission** so the runner can request an OIDC token:\n\n```yaml\npermissions:\n  id-token: write   # required for OIDC\n  contents: read\n```\n\n**Replace the `dotnet nuget push` step.** Remove the API key and use `--source` with the trusted-publisher endpoint:\n\n```yaml\n# BEFORE\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }} --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n\n# AFTER\n- uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4    # ensure v4+\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n  env:\n    NUGET_AUTH_TOKEN: ''            # not needed; OIDC handles auth\n```\n\nActually, the simplest approach with `setup-dotnet@v4`:\n\n```yaml\n- uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n  with:\n    source-url: https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source nuget.org\n```\n\nThe action automatically exchanges the OIDC token for a short-lived NuGet publish token — **no secret required**.\n\n### 3. Remove the secret\nOnce verified, delete `NUGET_API_KEY` from your repo's **Settings → Secrets**.\n\n---\n\n**Key points:**\n- `id-token: write` permission is mandatory\n- `setup-dotnet@v4+` handles the OIDC token exchange\n- The NuGet.org trusted-publisher config must match your repo/workflow exactly\n- No API key is stored or passed anywhere\n\nWant me to modify a specific workflow file if you can point me to it?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f62cd826-3e1d-4cf7-b8c4-844ae36766a8","outputTokens":564,"requestId":"040A:4010A:451F3A:50E6E6:69F0050A"},"id":"f2b891ce-3472-4274-b33a-a3c52a609b9b","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:53:43.098Z","parentId":"156b3a01-50fa-415d-8233-b18aac597e64"}
